---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SimplePromptTool from '../components/SimplePromptTool';
import { generateGeminiPrompt } from '../utils/promptTransformers';

Astro.response.headers.set('Cache-Control', 's-maxage=300, stale-while-revalidate=3600');
---
<Layout
  title="Free Gemini Prompt Generator — Get Better Results from Google Gemini"
  description="Transform your ideas into expertly crafted Gemini prompts. Free Gemini prompt generator that adds structure, context, and output specifications. No sign-up required."
>
  <div id="root">
    <SimplePromptTool
      client:only="react"
      seoTitle="Gemini Prompt Generator"
      seoDescription="Generate expertly structured Gemini prompts for clearer, more detailed responses."
      inputPlaceholder="Describe what you need from Gemini... e.g. explain quantum computing in simple terms with real-world examples"
      buttonLabel="Generate Gemini Prompt"
      transform={generateGeminiPrompt}
    />
  </div>

  <div class="px-6 py-12 space-y-6">
    <div class="text-center space-y-3 py-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a]">Gemini Prompt Generator</h1>
      <p class="text-[#6b6559] text-base max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Built for Google Gemini, this free tool transforms your simple ideas into expertly crafted prompts that get clearer, more detailed, and accurate responses from Google Gemini. Our Gemini prompt generator adds intelligent structure, crystal-clear instructions, rich context, and output format specifications.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="border border-[#c8c0a8] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">Why Use a Gemini Prompt Generator?</h2>
        <p class="text-[#6b6559] text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Google Gemini is powerful but responds best to structured, well-formatted prompts. Our free Gemini prompt generator takes your plain request and adds the structure Gemini needs — numbered response sections, evidence requirements, practical examples, and actionable recommendations. Get custom-made responses instead of generic answers every time.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-[#c8c0a8] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">What Gets Added to Your Gemini Prompt</h2>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5">📐</span><p class="text-[#6b6559] text-sm">Structured response format with numbered sections</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5">🔍</span><p class="text-[#6b6559] text-sm">Evidence and reasoning depth requirements</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5">💡</span><p class="text-[#6b6559] text-sm">Request for practical examples and use cases</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5">🚀</span><p class="text-[#6b6559] text-sm">Actionable next steps and recommendations</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border border-[#c8c0a8] rounded-xl p-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] text-sm">Is this Gemini prompt generator free?</p>
          <p class="text-[#6b6559] text-xs mt-1">Yes — completely free, no sign-up required. Generate unlimited Gemini prompts.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] text-sm">Does it work with Gemini 2.0 and Gemini Ultra?</p>
          <p class="text-[#6b6559] text-xs mt-1">Yes. Structured prompts work with all Gemini versions, and also improve results in ChatGPT, Claude, and other AI models.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] text-sm">What kinds of tasks can I use this for?</p>
          <p class="text-[#6b6559] text-xs mt-1">Research, writing, analysis, coding, brainstorming, explanations — any task where you want a more thorough, structured response from Gemini.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] text-sm">Is Gemini better than ChatGPT for writing?</p>
          <p class="text-[#6b6559] text-xs mt-1">Both are capable writing tools, but they have different strengths. Google Gemini tends to produce well-structured, factually grounded content with strong research integration, while ChatGPT often shines in conversational tone and creative variation. The best results from either model come from well-structured prompts — which is exactly what this generator produces. You can also try our <a href="/chatgpt-prompt-generator" class="text-[#1a1a1a] underline hover:no-underline">ChatGPT prompt generator</a> to compare outputs side by side.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] text-sm">What's the best way to prompt Gemini 3?</p>
          <p class="text-[#6b6559] text-xs mt-1">Gemini 3 responds well to structured prompts that include clear role framing, numbered output sections, and explicit evidence requirements — the same patterns this generator applies automatically.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center text-xs text-[#6b6559] pb-2">
      Also try: <a href="/chatgpt-prompt-generator" class="text-[#1a1a1a] underline hover:no-underline">ChatGPT Prompt Generator</a> · <a href="/claude-prompt-generator" class="text-[#1a1a1a] underline hover:no-underline">Claude Prompt Generator</a>
    </div>

    <a href="#root" class="block w-full py-4 bg-[#f0b429] border-2 border-[#1c1c1c] rounded-xl text-center font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] text-lg hover:brightness-95 transition-all">
      Generate Your Gemini Prompt
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>
